Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.04,0:00:00.24,Default,,0,0,0,,That's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:02.04,0:00:02.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:02.96,0:00:04.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Something kinda surprising happened.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:05.48,0:00:10.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Alright, so from now on, I'd like to introduce some messages from our listeners!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:10.48,0:00:13.12,Default,,0,0,0,,First up, we got a message from Happy Name Eyal-san!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:13.12,0:00:14.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you so much!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:14.24,0:00:15.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Good evening, Date-chan!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.12,0:00:15.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Good evening!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.96,0:00:18.72,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm a fan from overseas, and I'm studying Japanese.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.24,0:00:21.76,Default,,0,0,0,,I look forward to hearing Sayuri-san's voice every week.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.12,0:00:24.68,Default,,0,0,0,,I really love your radio show and the fun segments.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.72,0:00:25.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.60,0:00:33.88,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm a grad student in a doctoral program, researching new cancer treatments and therapies using AI.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.20,0:00:36.56,Default,,0,0,0,,This research is really rewarding, and I'm enjoying it a lot.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.04,0:00:38.76,Default,,0,0,0,,I have something I'd like to ask you, Sayuri-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:39.24,0:00:44.24,Default,,0,0,0,,If you were to go to university after high school, what field would you want to study?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.28,0:00:45.08,Default,,0,0,0,,That's what they asked!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.08,0:00:46.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:46.56,0:00:49.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Wow, from overseas! Thank you so much!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:49.76,0:00:50.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Thanks for listening!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.00,0:00:52.40,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm so happy! Are you doing okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.40,0:00:55.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Am I speaking proper Japanese, I wonder?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.56,0:00:57.88,Default,,0,0,0,,You don't need to learn words like 'yabai,' you know.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:58.16,0:01:02.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, you don't have to remember phrases like 'yabai' or 'yabai jan'.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:04.04,0:01:04.60,Default,,0,0,0,,But, uh,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:05.20,0:01:06.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Keep up the good work!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:06.56,0:01:07.60,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm rooting for you!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:08.00,0:01:11.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Wow, cancer treatments and therapies using AI!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:12.20,0:01:13.08,Default,,0,0,0,,That's amazing!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:13.08,0:01:22.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, I actually didn't go to university, but when I was in my first and second year of high school, you know,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:23.60,0:01:49.52,Default,,0,0,0,,I was interested in going to a university for psychology. My future dreams were still vague back then, I wasn't dead set on one thing. But I really wanted to be a school counselor, you know!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.00,0:02:09.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, I was interested in that around my first and second year of high school. When you look up 'school counselor,' it always says you need to study psychology. So I vaguely thought it'd be nice to study something like that back then.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.96,0:02:10.80,Default,,0,0,0,,But you never know, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.80,0:02:32.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Even if you decide to become a school counselor and go into psychology, you might suddenly find another path interesting while you're in university. I know a lot of people around me who were thinking of going into psychology. I feel like psychology is a pretty broad field.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.40,0:02:34.80,Default,,0,0,0,,At least when I looked into it.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.12,0:02:35.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.00,0:02:47.16,Default,,0,0,0,,And also, I was super interested in hair and makeup, maybe at a university or vocational school. I really loved makeup, you see.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.60,0:03:05.60,Default,,0,0,0,,So I looked into vocational schools for hair and makeup. I don't know all the details, but many schools teach both hair and makeup together. I love makeup, but I'm absolutely terrible at hair styling.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.60,0:03:13.36,Default,,0,0,0,,I can't even do my own hair, let alone someone else's. My hands are just so clumsy!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.88,0:03:21.44,Default,,0,0,0,,So, even though I really wanted to go, I figured it was impossible for me and gave up.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.76,0:03:24.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, I just thought, 'I can't do this.'
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.72,0:03:29.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, I was super interested, but even now, I still love makeup!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.64,0:03:30.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you so much!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.52,0:03:31.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Uh, yeah, keep up the great work!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.68,0:03:32.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's do our best together!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.72,0:03:34.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Alright, next up, Happy Name...
